Description: Implements a probabilistic principal component analysis (PPCA) based model for normalizing data from multiple platforms. This package is particularly useful for integrating and normalizing high-dimensional biological data, such as gene expression data from different microarray or sequencing platforms. It provides functions for model training, prediction, and evaluation, including cross-validation and parameter estimation.
